Spy in Cigarette - Python MITM Attack & Network Scanner

Spy in Cigarette is a Python tool that allows you to scan your network for connected devices and perform Man-in-the-Middle (MITM) attacks. It also features a loading screen to provide a smooth and professional user experience while the script is running.

